name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Uh, yeah, I think we've hit dream bedrock here, Morty. It's time to make our move.

name: Agent
line: Make it bounce.

name: Rick
line: No, you didn't.

name: Agent
line: Oh, man.

name: Rick
line: What the hell is wrong with you people?! You're always picking on me and now you're trying to make me feel bad.

name: Agent
line: You're the worst.

name: Rick
line: Aw, man! Oh, man, man...

name: Agent
line: I know. I know. It makes me sad to see another Rick cop buying into his sensitivity training.

name: Rick
line: It's okay, Morty, I know you were acting crazy. I mean, it's okay to laugh at myself.

name: Agent
line: Well, I mean he kind of had to in order to get out of school.

name: Rick
line: I was also part of the school's test line of defense against the evil Grampa family.

name: Agent
line: Morty, I'm not proud to share this, but the truth is I just kept crawling, and it kept working.

name: Rick
line: Alright, Morty! We're goners now!

name: Agent
line: Yeah, Morty...

name: Rick
line: Y-You know what? I-I'm really bad at this.

name: Agent
line: Good thing I saw that note.

name: Rick
line: If you keep coming at me, I'll talk to you later.

name: Agent
line: Come on, Morty?

name: Rick
line: Yeah. You know what, Morty is this stuff that you keep slipping into your subconscious? You know, that's what's important.

name: Agent
line: Yeah... I know what's crucial to keep you coming at you.
